{"id": "art-43", "label": "Art. 43", "title": "Art. 43: Lipsa capacităţii de exerciţiu", "slug": "art-43", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 43: Lipsa capacit&#259;&#355;ii de exerci&#355;iu </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>În afara altor cazuri prev&#259;zute de lege, nu au capacitate de\nexerci&#355;iu:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)minorul\ncare nu a împlinit vârsta de 14 ani;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_68107706\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1294\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_68107706\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)cel care beneficiaz&#259; de m&#259;sura tutelei\nspeciale.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_248572122\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1293\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_248572122\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Pentru cei care nu au capacitate de exerci&#355;iu,\nactele juridice se încheie, în numele acestora, de reprezentan&#355;ii lor\nlegali, în condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute de lege.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1952723912\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1292\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1952723912\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Cu toate acestea,\npersoana lipsit&#259; de capacitatea de exerci&#355;iu poate încheia\nsingur&#259; actele anume prev&#259;zute de lege, actele de conservare, precum\n&#351;i actele de dispozi&#355;ie de mic&#259; valoare, cu caracter curent\n&#351;i care se execut&#259; la momentul încheierii lor. Dispozi&#355;iile art.\n168 alin. (4) r&#259;mân aplicabile.</b></span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><u><span style='color:#569748'>*) Prin Decizia nr. 58/2024\nÎnalta Curte de Casa&#355;ie &#351;i Justi&#355;ie admite sesizarea pentru\npronun&#355;area unei hot&#259;râri prealabile, &#351;i, în\nconsecin&#355;&#259;, stabile&#351;te c&#259;, în interpretarea\ndispozi&#355;iilor art. 43 alin. (3) din Codul civil, acceptarea expres&#259; a\nmo&#351;tenirii de c&#259;tre un minor lipsit de capacitate de exerci&#355;iu\nreprezint&#259; un act de dispozi&#355;ie &#351;i necesit&#259;\nîncuviin&#355;area instan&#355;ei de tutel&#259;.</span></u><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_530400314\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1291\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_530400314\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Actele pe care cel lipsit de capacitate de\nexerci&#355;iu le poate încheia singur pot fi f&#259;cute &#351;i de\nreprezentantul s&#259;u legal, în afar&#259; de cazul în care legea ar dispune\naltfel sau natura actului nu i-ar permite acest lucru.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}